"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"mobipreview.htm?31/33/32280?source=see_link\">",
"      Shoulder impingement syndrome",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <br/>",
"     The following organizations also provide reliable health information.",
